description: SQUID PRO QUO is the second can in the Baby Dictators series. It is created by artist / surfing teacher / oyster farmer / shark commentator, Andy Jacob in Wellfleet MA. Andy is one of the founders of this series, the purpose of which is to explore the alternate potential futures of baby Trump, had he only had a happier childhood. Andy took the concept of the series literally. The five surfer Trumps pulling SQUID PRO QUO in the artwork are alternate reality future Trumps who benefited from surfing lessons as kids and now live peacefully as professional surfers, riding the swells.
merch_types: museum quality prints, hoodies and stickers
name: Squid Pro Quo

by Andrew Jacob

description: BALLOON FACTORY is the first can in the Baby Dictators series. Created by Adam O’Day who lived for a time in Athens Georgia, we wanted the first beer in this series to take a step back from a literal rendering of the subject and to tell a different story… the BALLOON FACTORY is a pretty dark place, from which the balloon escapes to greener pastures.
merch_types: the original artwork, T-shirts and stickers
name: Balloon Factory

by Adam O'Day
